{"tid":2065930,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：不會直接取消限聚令","createTime":"2020-06-16T02:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T05:14:11.000Z","uid":212626,"like":26,"dislike":289,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3889567eaff9a3a953158fcd27378bde4c062e","tid":2065930,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥指，下午食衛局會公布放寬一些社交距離措施，她指由於疫情趨於穩定，市民亦熱切希望有社交活動，<span style=\"color: red;\">方向應是循序放寬，限聚令不會放寬到無限制</span>，提及北京和海外近日都有確診個案發生，所以放寬工作要好小心。林鄭月娥指，隨著進一步放寬保持社交距離的措施，加上政府星期日起，接受合資格人士申領1萬元現金補貼，希望市民多增加本地消費。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1310837&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1310837%26csid%3D261_341&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7o26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=4feb2e29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1310837&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"1a2b5f2103479605dcc8743fc70618e0057f0fe8","tid":2065930,"uid":8308,"like":125,"dislike":3,"score":122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:35:56.000Z","msg":"得啦 明啦<br />\n終於用就用啊嘛"},{"pid":"f850dd05ce6532818c7fc40cf73d7d4b1588a0f9","tid":2065930,"uid":132587,"like":135,"dislike":2,"score":133,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"想等國安法同限聚令無縫交接<br />\n算撚數啦<br />\n有無我地都係咁出架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f32c56bea9bbd0f6894a37b0c6bd06f43cc704","tid":2065930,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1042c1a5e571150498667fb922ff6fbad0880a9","tid":2065930,"uid":8858,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"維穩大於一切<img src=\"/assets/f